999", "traits": "Vigorous, stout semi-erect canes, semi-evergreen, good heat adaptation", "flesh_fruit": "", "yield_notes": "Very high yields, reliable in warm climates", "growing_notes": "EXCELLENT for Kerala. Recommended by Neva Plantations. Requires only 250 chill hours. Large, flavorful berries. Performs well in temperatures up to 38°C. Good for both home gardens and commercial production in Kerala.", "availability": "Neva Plantations (Kerala delivery), Kerala online nurseries", "sort_order": 1}, {"name": "Misty", "slug": "misty", "lineage_type": "hybrid", "climate_slug": "tropical-monsoon", "origin": "University of Florida, USA, 1989", "traits": "Upright vigorous growth, semi-evergreen, adaptable", "flesh_fruit": "", "yield_notes": "High productivity, reliable bearer", "growing_notes": "GOOD for Kerala (may need some protection in hottest months). Recommended by Neva Plantations for warmer Kerala regions. Reliable tropical performer with 400 chill hours. Balance of cold tolerance and heat adaptability. Moderate climate zones.", "availability": "Neva Plantations, Indian nurseries delivering to Kerala", "sort_order": 2}, {"name": "Sharp Blue", "slug": "sharp-blue", "lineage_type": "hybrid", "climate_slug": "tropical-monsoon", "origin": "University of Florida, USA, 1976", "traits": "Upright spreading, nearly evergreen in warm climates, vigorous", "flesh_fruit": "", "yield_notes": "Productive, versatile, late bearing extends season", "growing_notes": "", "availability": "", "sort_order": 3}, {"name": "Sunshine Blue", "slug": "sunshine-blue", "lineage_type": "hybrid", "climate_slug": "tropical-monsoon", "origin": "University of Florida breeding program, USA, 1990s", "traits": "Compact dwarf (1-1.5m), semi-evergreen, tolerates higher pH, ornamental", "flesh_fruit": "", "yield_notes": "Good productivity, reliable", "growing_notes": "", "availability": "", "sort_order": 4}, {"name": "Robin Blue", "slug": "robin-blue", "lineage_type": "hybrid", "climate_slug": "tropical